      <title>[신문으로 배우는 실용한자] 소명(疏明)</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/chinese_character/2026/01/13/5HVWR6DQEJDVFMJH7KKYZC663Y/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/chinese_character/2026/01/13/5HVWR6DQEJDVFMJH7KKYZC663Y/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
